Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望聖誕老人送你什麼禮物啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.39,0:00:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快點想好可就要來不及咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是從很遠的地方來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 說說現在最想要什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lop Ear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.55,0:00:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 那個不是有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想要個朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.07,0:01:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.24,0:01:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.27,0:01:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕樹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...工作上用的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把聖誕樹立起來好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.15,0:02:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是裝在樹頂上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家沒有煙囪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.66,0:02:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人能進來的 安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我把門鎖打開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.36,0:02:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.56,0:02:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}致聖誕老人 感謝您的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那胡蘿蔔是幹什麼的啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給馴鹿的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要關燈咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人只會給睡著的孩子送禮物喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 那快點關燈!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也好想見聖誕老人一面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,璘 吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還要謝謝馴鹿


